AI-Web-Crawler/
├── app/
│   ├── __init__.py
│   ├── main.py                   # Main Streamlit application entry point
│   ├── crawler.py                # Web crawling functionality
│   ├── processor.py              # Content processing and filtering
│   ├── storage.py                # Knowledge base and vector storage
│   ├── ollama_integration.py     # Integration with Ollama for Q&A
│   ├── utils.py                  # Utility functions
│   └── config.py                 # Configuration settings
├── data/
│   ├── crawled/                  # Raw crawled data
│   └── knowledge_base/           # Processed knowledge base data
├── static/
│   └── css/                      # CSS for Streamlit customization
│   └── img/                      # Images including logo placeholder
├── Dockerfile                    # Docker configuration
├── docker-compose.yml            # Docker Compose configuration
├── requirements.txt              # Python dependencies
├── setup.py                      # Package setup
├── .env.example                  # Example environment variables
└── README.md                     # Documentation